title: Mock Dishwasher Part 1 - DWSX0001
description: This is a simulated dishwasher part used to demonstrate AI integration. It's part 1 in our mock set.
installation: To install Dishwasher Part 1, turn off water supply, remove screws from base panel, replace the part and reconnect hoses.
troubleshooting: Resolves issues like water not draining, abnormal noise, or spray arm not spinning related to Dishwasher Part 1.
